org.codice.ddf.catalog.content.monitor

Class FileSystemPersistenceProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.catalog.content.monitor.FileSystemPersistenceProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.core.MapLoader<String,Object>, com.hazelcast.core.MapStore<String,Object>

    public class FileSystemPersistenceProvider
extends Object
implements com.hazelcast.core.MapLoader<String,Object>, com.hazelcast.core.MapStore<String,Object>
    Hazelcast persistence provider implementation of @MapLoader and @MapStore to serialize and persist Java objects stored in Hazelcast cache to disk.

    NOTE: The usage of object serialization/deserialization may trigger static analysis warnings. This usage is acceptable as the read/write directory is not configurable and lives under DDF_HOME.
